Mɨrɨ a'tai, apono' amʉ' ene'pʉ uya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipo'ne iyereutapɨ'sa' kon kamoro eke pe to' e'to' pe eseru aimenkanin nan pe irepasa' kon. I'mʉrʉpɨ'sa' kon a'kwarʉ kanan ene'pʉ uya i'napairon Sises nenpoika'pʉ ekama to' uya pɨkɨrɨ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa Maimu pɨkɨrɨ. Ene apurɨpɨ'sa' to' uya pʉra iyesi, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipe ika'sa' ene ma'kʉʉi eposa' to' uya pʉra iyesi tʉpee'pɨ kon pɨ', mɨrɨ pe pʉra temiyatʉ kon pɨ'. Mɨrɨpan kon e'mʉ'sa'kasa' terikʉ kon tʉpo esi'pʉ kin pe Kʉrai pokon pe 1,000 kaisa rɨ wʉipiya.
